scan.name: Baseline evaluation of 4 models
scan.description: This evaluation compares the robustness, accuracy, fairness and explanations for 4 candidate models.

model_use_case.name: Banking: Loan Approval
model_use_case.description:
In this use case, each entry in the dataset represents a person who takes a credit loan from a bank. The learning task is to classify each person as either a good or bad credit risk according to the set of attributes.

This dataset was sourced from Kaggle: https://www.kaggle.com/uciml/german-credit

The original source is: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Statlog+%28German+Credit+Data%29
model_use_case.author: info@cognitivescale.com

model.name: Multi-Layer Perceptron Classifier
model.description: Scikit-learn neural network MLP Classifier with 2 hidden layers using adam stochastic gradient-based optimizer
